---
import StarlightPage from '@astrojs/starlight/components/StarlightPage.astro';
---

<StarlightPage frontmatter={{ title: 'Contact', description: 'Contact options for the VISCERIUM Codex.' }}>
  <section class="support-page support-page--contact">
    <header class="support-hero codex-frame">
      <p class="codex-kicker">Private contact</p>
      <h1>Contact us</h1>
      <p>
        The private contact form is temporarily paused while the Codex deployment is kept on Cloudflare Pages.
        Public, trackable issues can still be opened through GitHub.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="support-note codex-frame">
      <h2>Use GitHub for public site issues</h2>
      <p>
        For typos, broken links, site bugs, feature requests, or content corrections, use the public support routes.
        This keeps the work visible and easier to track.
      </p>
      <a class="support-button" href="/support/">Open support page</a>
    </section>

    <section class="support-note codex-frame">
      <h2>Private messages</h2>
      <p>
        For collaboration, rights, credit, or sensitive concerns, private contact will return once the form is moved to
        a separate Worker endpoint that will not interfere with the static Codex deployment.
      </p>
    </section>
  </section>
</StarlightPage>
